==Ancient Greek==

===Etymology===
*A primary preposition; 

===Pronunciation===
*πρό / pro / pro 

===Preposition===
'''πρό'''

#“[[fore]]”, that is, in front of, [[prior]] (figuratively [[superior]]) to. 
#*In compounds it retains the same significations: 
#* [[above]], [[ago]], [[before]], or ever.

